source: <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MetaMask</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.js" integrity="sha256-2Kok7MbOyxpgUVvAk/HJ2jigOSYS2auK4Pfzbm7uH60=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
     <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.1.min.js"></script>

    <style>
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body{
           font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        }
        .head-container{
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            width: 60%;
            margin: 10px auto;
        }
        .select-box select, .typeSelect select{
            padding: 7px 10px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            width: 200px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-family: inherit;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        .typeSelect select{
            width: 250px;
        }
        .mainbox-container, .form-mainbox{
            border: 1px solid #d6d9dc;
            width: 45%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            margin-top: 80px;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }
        .form-mainbox{
            text-align: center;
        }
        .headBox h2 {
             font-size: 30px;
             text-align: center;
        }
        .headBox p{
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .headBox a {
            color: #0379ce;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .typeBox1{
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .typeText h3 {
            font-size: 17px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .infoBox{
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #E6F2FA;
            padding: 5px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            border-left: 5px solid#0376C9;
        }
        .infoText p{
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .inpBox label{
            display: block;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }
        .inpBox{
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .inpBox input{
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid #afafaf;
            padding: 15px 10px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-family: inherit;
        }
        .inpBox input:focus{
            border: none;
            outline: 1px solid #0376C9;
        }
        .inpBox svg{
            margin-left: 3px;
        }
        .infoBoxImg img{
            display: inline-block;
            transform: translateY(3px);
        }
        .inpMainBox{
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            grid-gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .btn12Box{
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
         .btn12Box button{
             background-color: #0379ce;
            font-family: inherit;
            padding: 17px 50px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            border: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
         }
        .btn12Box button:disabled{
            background-color: #81BAE4;
            font-family: inherit;
            padding: 17px 50px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            border: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .inpBox img {
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-left: 3px;
        }
        .hide{
            display: none !important;
        }
        .errorBox{
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: rgb(251,235,237);
            padding: 10px 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-left: 5px solid #D73847;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .errImg img {
            transform: translateY(3px);
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .btnUnder {
            background-color: #0379ce;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-family: inherit;
            border: none;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .loader,
        .loader:after {
        border-radius: 50%;
        width: 5em;
        height: 5em;
        }
        .loader {
        font-size: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin: 10px auto;
        text-indent: -9999em;
        border-top: .6em solid transparent;
        border-right: .6em solid #f8883b;
        border-bottom: .6em solid #f8883b;
        border-left: .6em solid #f8883b;
        -webkit-transform: translateZ(0);
        -ms-transform: translateZ(0);
        transform: translateZ(0);
        -webkit-animation: load8 .6s infinite linear;
        animation: load8 .6s infinite linear;
        text-align: center;
        }
        @-webkit-keyframes load8 {
        0% {
            -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);
            transform: rotate(0deg);
        }
        100% {
            -webkit-transform: rotate(360deg);
            transform: rotate(360deg);
        }
        }
        @keyframes load8 {
        0% {
            -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);
            transform: rotate(0deg);
        }
        100% {
            -webkit-transform: rotate(360deg);
            transform: rotate(360deg);
        }
        }
        .preloadBox{
            text-align: center;
        }
        .loader{
            text-align: center;
        }
        .loadImg{
            margin-left: 22px;
        }
        .preload{
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            background-color: #fff;
            z-index: 3000;
        }
        .preloadBox{
            position: absolute;
            top: 40%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 900px){
            .head-container, .mainbox-container{
                width: 95%;
            }
            .mainbox-container{
                margin-top: 40px;
            }
            .headBox h2 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            .headBox p{
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            .typeText h3 {
                font-size: 15px;
            }
            .typeSelect select{
                width: 100%;
            }
            .infoText p{
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            .btn12Box button, .btn12Box button:disabled{
               padding: 15px 20px;
            }
            .inpMainBox{
                display: block;
            }
            .inpBox{
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
            .select-box select{
                width: 100%;
            }
            .head-boxImg img{
                width: 130px;
            }

        }
        
    </style>
</head>
